-- Top Seed Sharapova Beats Pironkova to Reach Wimbledon 3rd Round
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2012-06-28T13:17:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-28/top-seed-sharapova-beats-pironkova-to-reach-wimbledon-3rd-round.html
No. 1 seed  Maria Sharapova  reached
the third round of the Wimbledon tennis tournament with a win
over Tsvetana Pironkova of Bulgaria.  The Russian won 7-6 (7-3), 6-7 (3-7), 6-0.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  